metadata.name: wiley's Willie Nelson & Janis Joplin Tribute Mural
metadata.description:
One of the most photographed murals in Austin, Texas and a major historical artifact, this NFT preserves the iconic culture of Texas legends Willie Nelson & Janis Joplin. Painted by Wiley Ross on the corner of 7th and Neches. The first collector of this augmented reality mural will have access to wiley via virtual hangout to hear the unique origin story of this work.

Collector can contact wiley to claim the virtual hangout here: https://wileyross.com/contact
